      "subject": "Chemistry",
      "section": "A",
      "questionType": "MCQ",
      "questionText": "<p>(I) 1,2-Dihydroxybenzene</p>\n<p>(II) 1,3-Dihydroxybenzene</p>\n<p>(III) 1,4-Dihydroxybenzene</p>\n<p>(IV) Hydroxy benzene</p>\n<p>The increasing order of boiling points of the above mentioned alcohols is</p>",
